chrysanthemums sa taglagas,

261
00:24:11,470 --> 00:24:12,310
at niyebe sa taglamig.

262
00:24:15,430 --> 00:24:16,340
Taon-taon,

263
00:24:17,670 --> 00:24:19,100
namuhay kami ng tahimik at ordinaryong buhay.

264
00:24:20,230 --> 00:24:22,790
♪Sa hanging silangan♪

265
00:24:25,510 --> 00:24:28,250
♪Sa buong panahon♪

266
00:24:28,260 --> 00:24:29,366
Gusto kong bumalik sa aming tahanan

267
00:24:33,190 --> 00:24:34,030
kasama mo.

268
00:24:34,690 --> 00:24:37,500
♪Ang lumang gabi♪

269
00:24:39,450 --> 00:24:46,410
♪Hiram ng mortal na init para maibsan ang lamig♪

270
00:24:47,260 --> 00:24:48,100
Sige.

271
00:24:50,390 --> 00:24:53,910
♪Paglalasap ng alak at magagandang sayaw♪

272
00:24:54,090 --> 00:25:00,910
♪Hayaan mo akong magmahal nang buong puso
sa kagandahang-loob ng kabataan♪

273
00:25:01,280 --> 00:25:09,330
♪Na may magaan, walang pakialam na mga salita,
kumikinang pa rin♪

274
00:25:09,670 --> 00:25:12,570
♪Kasama ka sa tabi ko♪

275
00:25:16,470 --> 00:25:17,780
Ang sarap talagang umuwi.

276
00:25:18,870 --> 00:25:20,020
Ito ang aking tahanan.

277
00:25:21,390 --> 00:25:22,383
Regalo sa akin iyon,

278
00:25:23,540 --> 00:25:24,630
kasama ang sarili ko.

279
00:25:26,550 --> 00:25:27,616
Ano ang gusto mong kainin?

280
00:25:27,836 --> 00:25:29,069
Ihahatid na kita para kumuha ng pagkain.

281
00:25:29,820 --> 00:25:30,660
Simu,

282
00:25:31,150 --> 00:25:31,990
mag isda tayo.

283
00:25:31,990 --> 00:25:36,060
♪Kung ipapaalam mo sa akin kung paano sasabihin♪

284
00:25:37,020 --> 00:25:38,230
Hindi ako marunong magluto ng isda.

285
00:25:38,230 --> 00:25:39,080
Pinili mo ang

286
00:25:39,090 --> 00:25:40,190
mga nakakalito na sangkap.

287
00:25:40,190 --> 00:25:41,540
Hindi pa ba sapat na kaya ko?

288
00:25:42,260 --> 00:25:43,580
Nagkakaroon kami ng buong fish banquet.

289
00:25:46,020 --> 00:25:53,310
♪Hiram ng mortal na init para maibsan ang lamig♪

290
00:25:54,340 --> 00:25:55,580
Parang hindi payag.

291
00:25:55,710 --> 00:25:56,670
Anong madulas na isda.

292
00:25:57,470 --> 00:25:58,310
Simu,

293
00:25:58,710 --> 00:25:59,550
tulungan mo akong magsandok nito.

294
00:26:01,470 --> 00:26:02,310
Subukan natin ito.

295
00:26:04,700 --> 00:26:07,690
♪Sa kagandahang-loob ng kabataan♪

296
00:26:07,930 --> 00:26:10,960
♪Na may magaan, walang pakialam na mga salita♪

297
00:26:12,780 --> 00:26:13,620
Simu,

298
00:26:15,500 --> 00:26:16,630
Gusto kong kasama ka.

299
00:26:17,440 --> 00:26:22,590
♪Isang palayok ng alak sa panandaliang panaginip♪

300
00:26:24,250 --> 00:26:32,620
♪Ang maikling buhay ay nangangahas na hanapin ang kawalang-hanggan♪

301
00:26:33,410 --> 00:26:39,410
♪Hiram ng isang magandang panaginip;
hayaan mong lasapin ko itong panandaliang kagalakan♪

302
00:26:39,870 --> 00:26:40,710
Your Grace,

303
00:26:41,910 --> 00:26:42,780
gusto mo pa ba

304
00:26:43,540 --> 00:26:45,020
ang bungo ko gaya ng ginawa mo

305
00:26:46,230 --> 00:26:47,430
noon?

306
00:26:49,780 --> 00:26:50,620
Oo.

307
00:26:51,820 --> 00:26:52,780
Gusto kitang maalala,

308
00:26:54,630 --> 00:26:55,470
ang iyong ngiti,

309
00:26:56,990 --> 00:26:57,870
ang bango mo,

310
00:26:59,540 --> 00:27:00,380
ang iyong mga kulay,

311
00:27:01,910 --> 00:27:02,870
at sa sandaling ito.

312
00:27:07,320 --> 00:27:09,890
♪Sa anong tahanan ako babalik♪

313
00:27:10,020 --> 00:27:10,860
Dakilang Ninuno...

314
00:27:14,340 --> 00:27:15,260
Tara na.

315
00:27:15,260 --> 00:27:16,100
Tumigil ka dyan.

316
00:27:17,630 --> 00:27:18,470
Halika dito.

317
00:27:20,780 --> 00:27:21,740
Dakilang Ninuno,

318
00:27:22,100 --> 00:27:23,060
iligtas ang aking buhay.

319
00:27:23,670 --> 00:27:24,510
Ako...

320
00:27:24,670 --> 00:27:25,710
kagagaling ko lang.

321
00:27:26,100 --> 00:27:27,630
Sobrang init pa ng mata ko,

322
00:27:28,230 --> 00:27:29,260
kaya hindi sila masyadong matalas.

323
00:27:30,580 --> 00:27:31,580
Wala man lang akong nakita.

324
00:27:33,260 --> 00:27:35,150
Dumating ako para maghatid ng gamot
kay Heneral Duan.

325
00:27:36,150 --> 00:27:38,100
Dinala ko lahat ng ito

326
00:27:38,100 --> 00:27:38,940
mula sa Starhaven Sect.

327
00:27:41,990 --> 00:27:43,190
Hindi na ako heneral.

328
00:27:44,230 --> 00:27:45,150
Dahil nandito ka,

329
00:27:45,740 --> 00:27:46,950
manatili para sa isang simpleng pagkain.

330
00:27:47,190 --> 00:27:48,030
Hindi, hindi.

331
00:27:48,430 --> 00:27:50,430
Hindi kita iistorbohin. Paalam.

332
00:27:50,470 --> 00:27:51,580
Magluluto ako ngayon.

333
00:27:52,710 --> 00:27:53,950
Ayaw mo ba ng lasa?

334
00:28:09,710 --> 00:28:10,550
Dakilang Ninuno,

335
00:28:11,300 --> 00:28:13,470
hindi mo siya tinatrato na parang pasyente,

336
00:28:15,580 --> 00:28:16,820
hindi rin ako tulad ng isang tao.

337
00:28:17,740 --> 00:28:19,470
Tapos gutom ka.

338
00:28:46,260 --> 00:28:47,100
Maganda ba?

339
00:29:03,060 --> 00:29:03,900
I'll go check on him.

340
00:29:10,020 --> 00:29:11,620
Ziji, umupo ka na at kumain.

341
00:29:26,060 --> 00:29:27,020
Hindi naman ganoon kalala.

342
00:29:28,260 --> 00:29:29,300
Ang sarap sa akin.

343
00:29:44,500 --> 00:29:45,340
anong mali?

344
00:29:46,580 --> 00:29:47,420
Tingnan mo, tingnan mo.

345
00:29:47,710 --> 00:29:48,820
Hindi naman masama, ha?

346
00:29:49,390 --> 00:29:50,340
Ibinato ko lang ang pagkain ko.

347
00:29:50,340 --> 00:29:51,320
Umuubo ka ng dugo.

348
00:29:52,740 --> 00:29:53,580
paano ito?

349
00:29:53,820 --> 00:29:54,800
May gamot ka ba?

350
00:29:55,230 --> 00:29:56,296
- Mayroon akong ilan.
- Ayos lang ako.

351
00:29:58,340 --> 00:29:59,280
Aling uri ang gusto mo?

352
00:30:00,260 --> 00:30:01,100
ayos lang ako.

353
00:30:02,710 --> 00:30:03,550
Gayunpaman,

354
00:30:06,470 --> 00:30:07,670
Mayroon akong isang pabor na hihilingin.

355
00:30:09,580 --> 00:30:10,420
ano gusto mo

356
00:30:14,580 --> 00:30:15,420
Halika dito.

357
00:30:16,870 --> 00:30:17,710
Lumapit ka.

358
00:30:25,190 --> 00:30:26,030
ano?

359
00:30:26,470 --> 00:30:27,310
Duan Shunxi.

360
00:30:29,020 --> 00:30:29,860
Duan Shunxi,

361
00:30:30,630 --> 00:30:31,990
Hindi ako kailanman

362
00:30:31,990 --> 00:30:32,830
nagkasala sa iyo.

363
00:30:32,840 --> 00:30:33,680
Bakit kailangan mo akong gawin

364
00:30:33,680 --> 00:30:34,560
hintayin ang aking katapusan

365
00:30:34,560 --> 00:30:35,450
bago ang Dakilang Ninuno?

366
00:30:49,300 --> 00:30:50,870
Lahat ng bagay sa mundong ito

367
00:30:51,430 --> 00:30:52,870
maglalaho balang araw.

368
00:30:54,300 --> 00:30:55,230
Your Grace,

369
00:30:55,990 --> 00:30:56,896
bakit mo siya pinipilit na manatili?

370
00:30:59,300 --> 00:31:00,340
Ito ang kanyang kapalaran.

371
00:31:01,300 --> 00:31:02,150
Wala sa iyong negosyo.

372
00:31:10,060 --> 00:31:11,190
Bilang Soberano ng Walang Kabuluhan,

373
00:31:12,260 --> 00:31:13,670
hindi ka maaaring manatili sa Mortal World.

374
00:31:15,100 --> 00:31:16,100
Bumalik ka kaagad.

375
00:31:17,470 --> 00:31:18,950
Kung gaano ka katagal mananatili

376
00:31:18,950 --> 00:31:19,910
sa Mortal World na ito,

377
00:31:21,670 --> 00:31:22,510
Walang kamatayan?

378
00:31:42,430 --> 00:31:43,270
Duan Shunxi,

379
00:31:44,990 --> 00:31:46,540
iiwan mo ang Dakilang Ninuno.

380
00:31:47,780 --> 00:31:48,820
Hindi ka ba malungkot?

381
00:31:53,950 --> 00:31:54,790
Sa buong buhay ko,

382
00:31:57,150 --> 00:31:58,540
mula sa unang pag-ibig hanggang sa araw ng aking kamatayan,

383
00:32:01,190 --> 00:32:02,780
Isang babae lang ang minahal ko.

384
00:32:07,260 --> 00:32:08,190
I count myself lucky.

385
00:32:10,910 --> 00:32:11,750
Ngayon,

386
00:32:13,710 --> 00:32:15,580
Ayokong malungkot ang mga huling araw ko.

387
00:32:21,390 --> 00:32:22,230
Gayunpaman,

388
00:32:22,670 --> 00:32:23,990
baka pag namatay ako,

389
00:32:26,540 --> 00:32:27,630
Kakapit ako sa kanya at iiyak.

390
00:33:12,470 --> 00:33:13,310
Pagkaalis ko,

391
00:33:14,670 --> 00:33:15,580
magdadalamhati ka ba para sa akin?

392
00:33:17,470 --> 00:33:18,740
Hahawakan mo ba ako at iiyak din?

393
00:33:25,910 --> 00:33:27,020
Sa lahat ng mga taon na ito,

394
00:33:29,100 --> 00:33:30,670
sa tuwing nababanggit ang aking kamatayan,

395
00:33:30,780 --> 00:33:31,990
wala kang sinasabi.

396
00:33:33,390 --> 00:33:34,230
Napaka-absurd.

397
00:33:35,260 --> 00:33:36,430
Ano ang iyong tinatakbuhan?

398
00:33:38,020 --> 00:33:39,230
Hindi ba ang kauri mo

399
00:33:39,910 --> 00:33:41,670
itakda itong maikling kapalaran

400
00:33:42,020 --> 00:33:43,100
para sa lahi ng Hejia,

401
00:33:44,260 --> 00:33:45,230
Walang kamatayan?

402
00:33:50,100 --> 00:33:50,980
Nanatili ka sa tabi ko

403
00:33:50,980 --> 00:33:52,260
at magbasa ng mga mortal nang maraming taon.

404
00:33:53,060 --> 00:33:53,900
Ngayon,

405
00:33:54,060 --> 00:33:56,230
sa tingin mo ba mali ang kauri mo?

406
00:33:58,190 --> 00:33:59,470
Ang mga imortal ay hindi nagkakamali.

407
00:34:00,630 --> 00:34:01,870
Kahit tama at mali ng mga mortal

408
00:34:02,540 --> 00:34:03,670
ay itinakda ng mga imortal.

409
00:34:07,710 --> 00:34:08,550
Oo.

410
00:34:08,950 --> 00:34:09,790
Napakatalino.

411
00:34:10,870 --> 00:34:12,140
Paanong mali ang mga imortal?

412
00:34:13,910 --> 00:34:14,950
Kung gayon bakit ka lumikha ng

413
00:34:14,950 --> 00:34:15,870
ang order na ito

414
00:34:15,870 --> 00:34:16,710
sa unang lugar?

415
00:34:17,870 --> 00:34:19,470
Para panatilihing balanse ang mundo

416
00:34:20,390 --> 00:34:21,910
at ligtas na kaligayahan para sa karamihan.

417
00:34:22,020 --> 00:34:22,860
Kaya,

418
00:34:23,220 --> 00:34:24,060
ikaw ay gumagamit ng

419
00:34:24,060 --> 00:34:24,990
ang ating kabaitan.

420
00:34:25,750 --> 00:34:26,590
Kami ay nanindigan

421
00:34:26,600 --> 00:34:27,660
ang kaligayahan ng marami.

422
00:34:27,990 --> 00:34:29,060
Ngunit wala kaming pagpipilian

423
00:34:29,060 --> 00:34:30,350
ngunit upang magdusa para dito.

424
00:34:30,790 --> 00:34:31,990
Bihisan mo ito ng marangal na salita

425
00:34:31,990 --> 00:34:32,950
habang pinapahirapan kami.

426
00:34:34,310 --> 00:34:35,456
Hindi mo ba nakikita ang yabang mo?

427
00:34:37,830 --> 00:34:38,670
Iyon ay

428
00:34:39,500 --> 00:34:40,750
bakit ako napunta dito.

429
00:34:43,500 --> 00:34:45,310
Kung wala ka pa ring nakikitang kasalanan sa iyong sarili,

430
00:34:46,310 --> 00:34:47,660
bumalik ka.

431
00:34:49,990 --> 00:34:50,830
Ziji,

432
00:34:51,580 --> 00:34:52,500
para magsalita ng malinaw,

433
00:34:54,350 --> 00:34:55,790
Pagod na ako sa larong ito.

434
00:35:01,750 --> 00:35:02,870
(Sampung taon sa tabi mo)

435
00:35:03,990 --> 00:35:04,830
(hanggang ngayon.)

436
00:35:07,540 --> 00:35:08,470
(Immortal,)

437
00:35:10,750 --> 00:35:11,750
(ililigtas mo ba ako?)

438
00:35:14,730 --> 00:35:18,350
♪Sa katahimikan, tinitigan kita♪

439
00:35:18,550 --> 00:35:22,280
♪Nakabit yung kamay ko tapos nalaglag♪

440
00:35:22,630 --> 00:35:26,190
♪Hayaan ang nananatiling hindi nasabi♪

441
00:35:27,030 --> 00:35:30,440
♪Bakit ganito ang pagpapahirap sa isa't isa?♪

442
00:35:30,720 --> 00:35:33,990
♪Ang hiling ko sana ay♪

443
00:35:35,060 --> 00:35:35,900
Ziji,

444
00:35:38,100 --> 00:35:39,270
sinunggaban mo ako.

445
00:35:39,760 --> 00:35:44,100
♪Naglaho sila na parang panaginip♪

446
00:35:45,750 --> 00:35:49,610
♪Daylight fades into ash♪

447
00:35:50,540 --> 00:35:52,259
(Ito ay higit sa isang buwan
mula noong sulat mo.)

448
00:35:53,220 --> 00:35:55,020
(Are you and Miss He both well?)

449
00:35:59,100 --> 00:35:59,950
(Kahit papaano,)

450
00:36:00,910 --> 00:36:02,270
(Madalas akong managinip)

451
00:36:02,270 --> 00:36:04,220
(ng pagkabata namin sa Daizhou.)

452
00:36:04,540 --> 00:36:06,820
(Daizhou)

453
00:36:08,470 --> 00:36:14,340
♪I-collapse ang bawat piraso♪

454
00:36:16,700 --> 00:36:19,550
♪I hate that I hesitated♪

455
00:36:19,550 --> 00:36:21,910
(Gayunpaman ang mga lumang araw ay maglalaho tulad ng ambon.)

456
00:36:21,910 --> 00:36:24,280
(Matalino at Determinado)

457
00:36:24,280 --> 00:36:26,270
♪Iniiwan ang lahat♪

458
00:36:26,310 --> 00:36:27,950
(Nahanap ko na ang gusto kong gawin.)

459
00:36:28,580 --> 00:36:29,620
(Sa ngayon, maayos na ang lahat.)

460
00:36:32,870 --> 00:36:34,700
(Kahit na ang buwan ay maaaring mag-wax at maghina,)

461
00:36:35,790 --> 00:36:37,310
(I still wish that you and Miss He)

462
00:36:37,620 --> 00:36:38,740
(maaaring kasing full ng buwan)

463
00:36:39,700 --> 00:36:40,790
(at mamuhay ng masaya.)

464
00:36:41,910 --> 00:36:43,950
(Ang iyong kapatid na babae, Jingyuan, magalang)

465
00:37:02,860 --> 00:37:06,020
(Ang iyong kapatid na babae, Jingyuan, magalang)

466
00:37:07,130 --> 00:37:10,640
♪Hayaan ang mga alaala na mawala♪

467
00:37:11,010 --> 00:37:13,680
♪Mag-isa, tinitipon ko sila♪

468
00:37:13,890 --> 00:37:18,340
♪Tulad ng mga talulot sa araw ng tagsibol♪

469
00:37:18,640 --> 00:37:22,200
♪Hanggang sa bumalik pa rin ang nakaraan♪

470
00:37:22,560 --> 00:37:26,120
♪At lumiwanag sa liwanag ng araw♪

471
00:37:26,310 --> 00:37:34,700
♪Bumalik ang hangin kasama ang aking mga pangarap♪

472
00:37:56,390 --> 00:37:57,680
Magpapadala ka ba ng tugon kay Jingyuan?

473
00:38:00,470 --> 00:38:02,060
Nahanap na niya ang gusto niyang gawin

474
00:38:03,270 --> 00:38:04,430
at nagsimula ng bagong buhay.

475
00:38:05,660 --> 00:38:07,060
Hindi ko na siya bibigyan ng higit na pag-aalala.

476
00:38:13,750 --> 00:38:14,590
Binanggit ni Jingyuan

477
00:38:14,590 --> 00:38:15,830
noong mga araw noon sa Daizhou.

478
00:38:20,020 --> 00:38:20,860
Sa tingin ko

479
00:38:22,990 --> 00:38:24,310
inalagaan niya si Xianye.

480
00:38:27,731 --> 00:38:28,965
Kung ang tagal nilang magkasama

481
00:38:28,976 --> 00:38:29,670
ay mas matagal,

482
00:38:31,870 --> 00:38:32,710
marahil...

483
00:38:44,399 --> 00:38:45,512
Marahil ito ay para sa pinakamahusay.

484
00:38:48,430 --> 00:38:49,830
Dapat niyang makalimutan sa lalong madaling panahon

485
00:38:52,430 --> 00:38:53,950
isang maikling, malabo na alaala.

486
00:38:57,390 --> 00:38:58,500
Paano niya nakalimutan?

487
00:39:00,140 --> 00:39:00,980
Hindi niya gagawin.

488
00:39:08,470 --> 00:39:10,180
Binati kami ni Jingyuan na kabilugan ng buwan.

489
00:39:12,433 --> 00:39:14,079
Ngunit nandito pa tayo,
at ang kabilugan ng buwan ay hindi.

490
00:39:16,953 --> 00:39:17,950
Sobrang tagal ko na

491
00:39:17,950 --> 00:39:18,993
hinangaan ang buwan kasama ka.

492
00:39:21,790 --> 00:39:22,790
Ang Mid-Autumn Festival

493
00:39:24,470 --> 00:39:25,500
ay masyadong malayo.

494
00:39:26,986 --> 00:39:28,492
Kung gusto mong ipagdiwang ang festival,

495
00:39:28,620 --> 00:39:29,470
magagawa natin ito anumang oras.

496
00:39:31,060 --> 00:39:31,900
Pero kung gusto mo

497
00:39:33,430 --> 00:39:34,620
upang humanga sa buwan...

498
00:39:39,350 --> 00:39:40,190
Sandali lang.

499
00:41:27,910 --> 00:41:28,750
Simu.

500
00:41:30,897 --> 00:41:32,917
Ang liwanag ng buwan sa ilalim ng araw
ay maganda, tama?

501
00:41:37,700 --> 00:41:38,540
gusto mo ba?

502
00:41:39,660 --> 00:41:40,500
ginagawa ko.

503
00:41:42,060 --> 00:41:43,020
lagi kong ginagawa.

504
00:42:10,680 --> 00:42:16,010
♪Sa pagitan ng itim at puti,
ripples crossed♪

505
00:42:16,340 --> 00:42:20,590
♪Light encountered shadow♪

506
00:42:21,950 --> 00:42:27,320
♪Natusok nito ang dilim at oras♪

507
00:42:27,620 --> 00:42:32,220
♪Ang hindi mababasag na kapalaran♪

508
00:42:33,310 --> 00:42:35,150
♪Biglang basag♪

509
00:42:47,360 --> 00:42:52,800
♪Sa pagitan ng itim at puti,
ripples crossed♪

510
00:42:52,980 --> 00:42:57,310
♪Light encountered shadow♪

511
00:42:58,680 --> 00:43:04,070
♪Natusok nito ang dilim at oras♪

512
00:43:04,300 --> 00:43:08,240
♪Ang hindi mababasag na kapalaran♪

513
00:43:10,010 --> 00:43:11,900
♪Biglang basag♪

514
00:43:14,560 --> 00:43:17,720
♪Makinig, umaatungal ang lahat ng tunog♪

515
00:43:17,720 --> 00:43:20,250
♪Habang ang malamig na yelo ay nagiging tides♪

516
00:43:20,250 --> 00:43:25,770
♪Ang kalungkutan ng isang siglo ay nakakatunaw ng mga pangarap♪

517
00:43:25,770 --> 00:43:29,010
♪Pagsunod sa patnubay ng tadhana♪

518
00:43:29,010 --> 00:43:33,870
♪Sa tadhana, ang ating mga sandali ay ipinagpalit♪

519
00:43:34,210 --> 00:43:37,230
♪Nagising ang puso bigla♪

520
00:43:37,230 --> 00:43:40,050
♪Panoorin ang pagbagsak ng mga paputok na parang bituin♪

521
00:43:40,310 --> 00:43:42,840
♪Ang bono na ito ay gusot sa isang thread♪

522
00:43:42,840 --> 00:43:48,260
♪Ang mga makamundong pagmuni-muni ay kumukupas sa ambon♪

523
00:43:48,430 --> 00:43:51,500
♪Pahiram ng isang panandaliang tibok ng puso♪

524
00:43:51,660 --> 00:43:56,560
♪Dinala mo ako sa mortal na alikabok,
hanggang sa nabighani ako sa mga alindog nito♪

525
00:43:56,770 --> 00:44:00,240
♪Ang puso ay nagising bigla♪

